divs: Sighting DetailsI aws walking my dogs the evening of March 25, 2001 @2315 hrs. when I heard astrange sound which I really could not identify. Then suddenly I saw a ship flyover me coming from the west and traveling east toward Binghamton NY. Theheight of the flight appeared to be between 200 to 300 ft above the hill I wason. My Larger dog became very curious. It appear that the craft had a shortfuselage and the wings were almost triangular. The total wing areas were lit upin a beige like light. Not normal for commercial aircraft. The speed of thecraft was slow. It appeared to be traveling under 100 mph. Craft of that sizewould have to travel faster even worth flaps down. I have remained very curiousabout this. There are 2 airports in close proximity, however, both were closedthat evening.Please contact me fpr more info. if you need me.
Summary: 11:15 PM saw low flying object going east.
